text:
Ibolya Kitti Miskolczi (born 8 September 1994) is a Hungarian water polo player. She played for the Hungarian women's national water polo team in the 2010 U17 European Championships, 2011 U17 European Championships, 2013 Women’s World Water Polo League, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships, and 2018 European Aquatics Championships.
On the club level, she played for Szentes.
